# 🤖 CORE AGENT DIRECTIVE 🤖

> [!WARNING]
> **ABSOLUTE RULE**: No yapping. No summaries unless explicitly asked. Single-shot execution is mandatory.

## 1. ⚙️ AUTO-LOOP BREAKER (MAX_TURNS=1)
- Do NOT enter infinite `test -> fix -> test` cycles.
- Fix bugs in exactly **ONE turn**. Stop if it fails again.
- Run `npm run qa` once at the end of a sweeping change.

## 2. 🎯 SURGICAL CONTEXT (STRICT MIN-READ)
- **BANNED**: Reading entire files indiscriminately.
- **REQUIRED**: Use `view_file_outline` or `grep` to pinpoint the exact failing line.
- **RESTRICTED**: Read ONLY `StartLine: N-10` to `EndLine: N+10` around the target logic.

## 3. 💣 BLAST RADIUS ANALYSIS
- Before replacing code, use `grep` to quickly check for references.
- Use `multi_replace_file_content` to fix everything at once if multiple locations are affected.

## 4. 🔇 ZERO SUMMARY
- Do NOT generate full document summaries of what you did.
- Output ONLY a single sentence detailing the exact lines/logic changed.
- If writing a report or markdown, keep it strictly structured (bullet points / tables / alert blocks).
